{"tid":447146,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《 盧根 》導演開始寫《 X-23 》外傳電影劇本","createTime":"2017-10-25T04:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T09:49:35.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fef67adb0a1afbef89543ceafecd533119552c","tid":447146,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"當曉治積曼卸下狼爪，決定放棄他一演便演了18年的《 變種特攻 》系列經典角色狼人之後，許多粉絲都關心會否有其他演員接演狼人，而大家確實也想不出有甚麼好的人選可以取代曉治積曼的地位。如果由小演員 Dafne Keen 飾演的角色 X-23 跟漫畫一樣接收狼人的名銜，應該就是普遍粉絲最受落的方案。<br />\n<br />\n終於，《狼人：武士激戰》、《盧根》導演占士曼高親口確定有以上的可能性，他已經着手編寫一部關於 X-23 的劇本，延續《盧根》之後的故事，這消息絕對讓《變種特攻》電影系列支持者或 Marvel 漫畫迷滿心驚喜。雖然電影公司仍未正式宣佈會開拍 X-23 外傳作品，但有導演高調參與令成事的機率大增。<br />\n<br />\n《變種特攻》系列未來還有多項計劃，包括已拍畢並於2018年上映的《新異變人》、《死侍2》及《X-Men: Dark Phoenix》，還有即將開拍的《Gambit》及《X-Force》。"},{"pid":"688a3d8f2497f255913760cb77eeaebb359c99fa","tid":447146,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"芒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553703f6a4774be2b0a2d5b9e789f4e724960b4c","tid":447146,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf91126d999b8b1e19fc3f3eda1ec4bc1cea1924","tid":447146,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"venom 都開拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b6fbd2bdbfce0a02e5688ec0d119f10c79adb1","tid":447146,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"拍多套.之後就出成年x23<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 